text: Louis Gompers (5 March 1902 - 22 October 1981) was a Dutch diver. He competed in the men's 3 metre springboard event at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1902 births Category:1981 deaths Category:Dutch male divers Category:Olympic divers of the Netherlands Category:Divers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Amsterdam
